org.fao.oekc.agris.inputRecords.parser

Class AgrisApSaxParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.fao.oekc.agris.inputRecords.parser.AgrisApSaxParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class AgrisApSaxParser
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    Parses Agris AP XML files. If the parameter globalDuplicatesRemoval is true, the parser checks for duplicates (based on titles) and generate new ARNS. If false, it does not check for duplicates and does not generate ARNs (which should be already in the data)
    Author:
    celli
